@author
Chris Williams (cwilli45)

@issues
- NONE

@notes
- Build on a CSL machine with "make" then run "a.out"

@controls
Move mouse = rotate camera
W/A/S/D = move camera
Q/E = lower/raise camera
SPACE = animate
R = reset world
I/J/L/K = move light
U/O = lower/raise light
P = change light's animation pattern (nothing OR sunrise/sunset OR move along floor)
